---
title: Zucchini and Asparagus Farro Bowl with Parmesan and Lemon
description: Farro has had something of a moment lately, becoming a favourite grain of chefs and home cooks alike for its nutty flavour, addictively chewy texture, and high-fibre content.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/zucchini-and-asparagus-farro-bowl-f32cc168.jpg
